name: Ex micro bikini
description:
I start a poll the model training in the future. This poll is open to everyone, so you can remain anonymous. https://www.patreon.com/posts/what-kind-of-do-83968613

The default micro bikini is not micro enough, So I made it a little bit smaller.

For realistic model it is not reduced enough, but you can still try.

V2 update note:

I gain more experience after I publish the v1 model, so it is a new one. If you are satisfied with the v1 model, you don't have to download v2, v2 is an experimental model. I am already satisfied with the v1 model.

The v1 model is iterative. The base imagines are from v0 (unpublished, fully based on 3D model imagines, if weighting up will look bad) generated.

The v2 model is not iterative. As same as v0, fully based on 3D model imagines, but with higher resolution (768*768), and more sample materials (25). I also try a more general training model anythingLoRA to train this model. If it works well, I think I will keep this method since it saves me a lot of time.
